# Admin + automation endpoints.
# Audit needs Admin:view (u-pnair Compliance / u-admin); running jobs needs Admin:edit (u-admin).

@host = http://localhost:8080

### Hash-chained audit log (kpis.chainValid re-verifies the chain)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/audit
X-User-Id: u-pnair

### Registered background jobs with next fire times
GET {{host}}/api/ops/jobs
X-User-Id: u-admin

### Fire the overdue-allocation sweep on demand
POST {{host}}/api/ops/jobs/overdue-allocation-sweep/run
X-User-Id: u-admin

### Fire the approval SLA monitor
POST {{host}}/api/ops/jobs/approval-sla-monitor/run
X-User-Id: u-admin

### Fire the custodian feed sync (recon scaffold)
POST {{host}}/api/ops/jobs/custodian-feed-sync/run
X-User-Id: u-admin

### RBAC negative check — Counsel has Admin: none → 403
GET {{host}}/api/admin/audit
X-User-Id: u-jokafor
